Question 0
Write a  script that creates a folder called "Bash Scripting "  and create all required files for this task (all at once) in this folder .
Lastly, print the folders content.

#!/bin/bash

# creates a folder called "Bash Scripting"
mkdir Bash_Scripting

# create all required files
touch 0x{0..20}

# print the folders content
ls
